header.gameNote: SAN DIEGO COUNTY CREDIT UNION HOLIDAY BOWL

videos.description: Feeling the pressure, Brian Lewerke scrambles then finds an open Cody White in the end zone for a 15-yard touchdown to give the Spartans' the lead.
videos.headline: Michigan State's Lewerke scrambles for TD

videos.description: Brian Lewerke throws a 49-yard pass down the field to a wide open Felton Davis and easily takes it to the end zone for a Spartan touchdown.
videos.headline: Michigan State's Lewerke goes deep for TD

videos.description: Brian Lewerke connects with Cody White for the second time tonight for a 10-yard touchdown to widen the Spartans lead over the Cougars.
videos.headline: Michigan State pads lead with TD

videos.description: Damion Terry finds a gap in the defense and takes it all the way home for a 6-yard Michigan State touchdown.
videos.headline: Spartans' Terry rushes for TD

videos.description: Washington State's Tyler Hilinski finds Davontavean Martin how makes a diving catch for a 14-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Cougars chips away at Spartans's lead with TD

videos.description: Davontavean Martin uses his speed to dive into the end zone and extend the ball over the pylon for a Cougars touchdown.
videos.headline: Washington State's Martin dives for TD
